item.obf_query:
t.row_id in (select act.row_id from crm_activity act
left join crm_ctc_act ca on ca.crm_ctcact_act_id = act.row_id
left join crm_contact ctc on ca.crm_ctcact_ctc_id = ctc.row_id
left join crm_account acc on acc.row_id = ctc.crm_ctc_acc_id
WHERE acc.row_id = [row_id])
